{"type":"message","id":"e06cb677","parentId":"e7c8b3a4","timestamp":"2026-05-04T02:23:47.106Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:6878985b-3761-4ad2-aa88-18ec445421e7 Wiki Logging - Agent X] Execute: python3 ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py x\n\nThis logs recent conversations to the wiki at ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/. Read the wiki-heartbeat.py script and follow its logic.\nCurrent time: Sunday, May 3rd, 2026 - 10:23 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-05-04 02:23 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777861427045}}
